    Class
    Description
    Canceled
    A concrete implementation of the State Class, representing the Canceled State of the WorkOrder, that is, when it's been waived by the Client.
    Created
    A concrete implementation of the State Class, representing the Created State of the WorkOrder, that is, when its just been registered by a Technician.
    Finished
    A concrete implementation of the State Class, representing the Finished State of the WorkOrder, that is, when all its Services have been completed.
    Open
    A concrete implementation of the State Class, representing the Open State of the WorkOrder, that is, when a Technician is taking care of it.
    Payed
    A concrete implementation of the State Class, representing the Payed State of the WorkOrder, that is, when the Invoice total has been completely paid.
    State
    Represents the base aspects of the State of the WorkOrders of the Assistance, by determining their basic capabilities/operations.
